Its an easy question to deflect.<p>- &quot;I don&#x27;t feel comfortable sharing that&quot;
- &quot;I&#x27;m still looking at a couple different options and don&#x27;t want to pigeon hole myself&quot;
- &quot;What salary is being offered with this position?&quot;<p>If they take issue with your non-response, its a (small) sign that you might headed towards a non-ideal working environment.
